'''MedFlash''' is a portable [[personal health record]] storage device developed and sold by Connectyx Technologies in the United States. Its primary purpose is for transporting and maintaining personal health records.

MedFlash is currently produced as a [[USB flash drive]], and is sold in all US states. MedFlash has special in case of emergency features on its members ID card so when you can't speak MedFlash speaks for you.

